a348ccff13fd037d7a270e1419a14c98e3d36dc7.title: Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice
a348ccff13fd037d7a270e1419a14c98e3d36dc7.synopsis: Fearing the actions of a god-like Super Hero left unchecked, Gotham City’s own formidable, forceful vigilante takes on Metropolis’s most revered, modern-day savior, while the world wrestles with what sort of hero it really needs. And with Batman and Superman at war with one another, a new threat quickly arises, putting mankind in greater danger than it’s ever known before.

07e5b0efa15351dfd166560b58533741301baae2.title: Batman Begins
07e5b0efa15351dfd166560b58533741301baae2.synopsis: Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.

0ea63994cf3531d4ec2fa9cf01e8adfff1903eac.title: The Lego Batman Movie
0ea63994cf3531d4ec2fa9cf01e8adfff1903eac.synopsis: In the irreverent spirit of fun that made "The Lego Movie" a worldwide phenomenon, the self-described leading man of that ensemble—Lego Batman—stars in his own big-screen adventure. But there are big changes brewing in Gotham, and if he wants to save the city from The Joker’s hostile takeover, Batman may have to drop the lone vigilante thing, try to work with others and maybe, just maybe, learn to lighten up.

f0276c1471035e8f738c7bdb13a45f2c720fe002.title: Batman
f0276c1471035e8f738c7bdb13a45f2c720fe002.synopsis: The Dark Knight of Gotham City begins his war on crime with his first major enemy being the clownishly homicidal Joker, who has seized control of Gotham's underworld.

a22966f7dbcec7cc0ca728e8658a993cc3ca2fa3.title: Batman Returns
a22966f7dbcec7cc0ca728e8658a993cc3ca2fa3.synopsis: Having defeated the Joker, Batman now faces the Penguin - a warped and deformed individual who is intent on being accepted into Gotham society. Crooked businessman Max Schreck is coerced into helping him become Mayor of Gotham and they both attempt to expose Batman in a different light. Selina Kyle, Max's secretary, is thrown from the top of a building and is transformed into Catwoman - a mysterious figure who has the same personality disorder as Batman. Batman must attempt to clear his name, all the time deciding just what must be done with the Catwoman.

c5e28ea37800e636b464f3341055ce745ac4d318.title: Batman Forever
c5e28ea37800e636b464f3341055ce745ac4d318.synopsis: The Dark Knight of Gotham City confronts a dastardly duo: Two-Face and the Riddler. Formerly District Attorney Harvey Dent, Two-Face believes Batman caused the courtroom accident which left him disfigured on one side. And Edward Nygma, computer-genius and former employee of millionaire Bruce Wayne, is out to get the philanthropist; as The Riddler. Former circus acrobat Dick Grayson, his family killed by Two-Face, becomes Wayne's ward and Batman's new partner Robin.

81bb5fb2f5875ecc1e263820aced8cf7b140d42d.title: Batman: The Killing Joke
81bb5fb2f5875ecc1e263820aced8cf7b140d42d.synopsis: As Batman hunts for the escaped Joker, the Clown Prince of Crime attacks the Gordon family to prove a diabolical point mirroring his own fall into madness.

33c8dd629ad131a0b527d8b3c4a8df3ccbcd0e1a.title: Batman & Robin
33c8dd629ad131a0b527d8b3c4a8df3ccbcd0e1a.synopsis: Along with crime-fighting partner Robin and new recruit Batgirl, Batman battles the dual threat of frosty genius Mr. Freeze and homicidal horticulturalist Poison Ivy. Freeze plans to put Gotham City on ice, while Ivy tries to drive a wedge between the dynamic duo.

0a160e7ca8bb656e3b85bf284320f44a04024a6d.title: Batman: The Dark Knight Returns, Part 1
0a160e7ca8bb656e3b85bf284320f44a04024a6d.synopsis: Batman has not been seen for ten years. A new breed of criminal ravages Gotham City, forcing 55-year-old Bruce Wayne back into the cape and cowl. But, does he still have what it takes to fight crime in a new era?

98c4178d28d7cea0bbe234d533d688795676576f.title: Batman: The Dark Knight Returns, Part 2
98c4178d28d7cea0bbe234d533d688795676576f.synopsis: Batman has stopped the reign of terror that The Mutants had cast upon his city.  Now an old foe wants a reunion and the government wants The Man of Steel to put a stop to Batman.

0f78c83297ad0783aa8d1a6d8f88d6fab4a7dc17.title: Batman: Under the Red Hood
0f78c83297ad0783aa8d1a6d8f88d6fab4a7dc17.synopsis: Batman faces his ultimate challenge as the mysterious Red Hood takes Gotham City by firestorm. One part vigilante, one part criminal kingpin, Red Hood begins cleaning up Gotham with the efficiency of Batman, but without following the same ethical code.

71e8e95427183a97efd7ed8b09d6b94def380c8a.title: Batman: Assault on Arkham
71e8e95427183a97efd7ed8b09d6b94def380c8a.synopsis: Based on the hit video game series, Batman must find a bomb planted by the Joker while dealing with a mysterious team of villains called, The Suicide Squad.

54754462a06f284c3b90852cb52d86b4f17c2aed.title: Batman: Bad Blood
54754462a06f284c3b90852cb52d86b4f17c2aed.synopsis: Bruce Wayne is missing. Alfred covers for him while Nightwing and Robin patrol Gotham City in his stead. And a new player, Batwoman, investigates Batman's disappearance.

4d745c3d294f37c74e201cb78e307d0617a67097.title: Batman Ninja
4d745c3d294f37c74e201cb78e307d0617a67097.synopsis: Gorilla Grodd's time displacement machine transports many of Batman's worst enemies to feudal Japan, along with the Dark Knight and a few of his allies.

4e6cccbdd91554ffc27ccfb0f95707f8351b3678.title: Son of Batman
4e6cccbdd91554ffc27ccfb0f95707f8351b3678.synopsis: Batman learns that he has a violent, unruly pre-teen son with Talia al Ghul named Damian Wayne who is secretly being raised by Ra's al Ghul and the League of Assassins. When Ra's al Ghul apparently dies after a battle with Deathstroke, Batman must work to stop his long-lost son from taking revenge and guiding him to a righteous path, in addition to the chance for the pair to truly acknowledging each other as family.

5be70c5db6a800b8ec01a48c91931fcfff084625.title: Batman: Year One
5be70c5db6a800b8ec01a48c91931fcfff084625.synopsis: Two men come to Gotham City: Bruce Wayne after years abroad feeding his lifelong obsession for justice and Jim Gordon after being too honest a cop with the wrong people elsewhere. After learning painful lessons about the city's corruption on its streets and police department respectively, this pair learn how to fight back their own way. With that, Gotham's evildoers from top to bottom are terrorized by the mysterious Batman and the equally heroic Gordon is assigned to catch him by comrades who both hate and fear him themselves. In the ensuing manhunt, both find much in common as the seeds of an unexpected friendship are laid with additional friends and rivals helping to start the legend.

0cba31e699b0a2cc10f00b640520f4821471eba6.title: Batman and Harley Quinn
0cba31e699b0a2cc10f00b640520f4821471eba6.synopsis: Batman and Nightwing are forced to team with the Joker's sometimes-girlfriend Harley Quinn to stop a global threat brought about by Poison Ivy and Jason Woodrue, the Floronic Man.

58611c054092665e48ccb4962ebc754f4de0e9ce.title: Batman: Gotham by Gaslight
58611c054092665e48ccb4962ebc754f4de0e9ce.synopsis: In an alternative Victorian Age Gotham City, Batman begins his war on crime while he investigates a new series of murders by Jack the Ripper.

fb03c19d1dff8be5b19da43266ff03956c970490.title: Superman/Batman: Apocalypse
fb03c19d1dff8be5b19da43266ff03956c970490.synopsis: Batman discovers a mysterious teen-aged girl with superhuman powers and a connection to Superman. When the girl comes to the attention of Darkseid, the evil overlord of Apokolips, events take a decidedly dangerous turn.

b0664fb2943a5b81e3faf72227dc722d3b32d299.title: Batman: Mask of the Phantasm
b0664fb2943a5b81e3faf72227dc722d3b32d299.synopsis: An old flame of Bruce Wayne's strolls into town, re-heating up the romance between the two. At the same time, a mass murderer with an axe for one hand begins systematically eliminating Gotham's crime bosses. Due to the person's dark appearance, he is mistaken for Batman. Now on the run, Batman must solve the mystery and deal with the romance between him and Andrea Beaumont.

d7a7334fa581d0b6a21539d71d8c87a19255c2a9.title: Superman/Batman: Public Enemies
d7a7334fa581d0b6a21539d71d8c87a19255c2a9.synopsis: United States President Lex Luthor uses the oncoming trajectory of a Kryptonite meteor to frame Superman and declare a $1 billion bounty on the heads of the Man of Steel and his ‘partner in crime’, Batman. Heroes and villains alike launch a relentless pursuit of Superman and Batman, who must unite—and recruit help—to try and stave off the action-packed onslaught, stop the meteor Luthors plot.

3146edc65321dba593f768faf7f3e58ab9d04de3.title: Batman & Mr. Freeze: SubZero
3146edc65321dba593f768faf7f3e58ab9d04de3.synopsis: When a desperate Mr. Freeze, to save his dying wife, kidnaps Barbara Gordon (Batgirl) as an involuntary organ donor, Batman and Robin must find her before the operation can begin.

21337b51f775ca8622f09ee34371f0224c3a83f3.title: Batman: Mystery of the Batwoman
21337b51f775ca8622f09ee34371f0224c3a83f3.synopsis: A new vigilante, Batwoman, is wreaking havoc in Gotham City. The dynamic duo must discover her true identity.

1b1e8b1e1d152b06ea599f18ee03df63c6d6d7c9.title: Batman vs. Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
1b1e8b1e1d152b06ea599f18ee03df63c6d6d7c9.synopsis: Batman, Batgirl and Robin forge an alliance with the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles to fight against the Turtles' sworn enemy, The Shredder, who has apparently teamed up with Ra's Al Ghul and The League of Assassins.

be53bb7c6f0481ab73c38e5ecd41fc3803676b05.title: Batman vs. Two-Face
be53bb7c6f0481ab73c38e5ecd41fc3803676b05.synopsis: Former Gotham City District Attorney Harvey Dent, one side of his face scarred by acid, goes on a crime spree based on the number '2'. All of his actions are decided by the flip of a defaced, two-headed silver dollar.

4cb384f3f2d4e142130f510c100612b6b26fdfdf.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws of Destiny

8aa28404c8814a0be3e1a9f26cd36df1ef319272.title: George Clarke's Old House, New Home

ae9420cd1125fb70b922c12462141bb1696d3015.title: Poor Boy
ae9420cd1125fb70b922c12462141bb1696d3015.synopsis: A little boy announces on his seventh birthday that he is a stranger named Danny, a grown man who died seven years earlier.

ce6aff9247c0f6b3b7b43c4890ec715d35c451cf.title: Bad Cat
ce6aff9247c0f6b3b7b43c4890ec715d35c451cf.synopsis: Produced by Turkey's biggest animation studio, Anima Istanbul, The Bad Cat is an animated epic for young adults featuring the unforgettably bad cat, Shero and his foul mouthed gang in action. As animals inhabiting streets Shero and his friends are after what anyone else in their notoriously sleazy Istanbul neighborhood wants: debauchery with girls, food and the occasional drinking binge. This ordinary looking day will prove otherwise as their paths cross with humans, things get a little out of hand in hilarious, harsh and unexpected ways.  The Bad Cat is an animated 3D feature film that strikes into our heads the epitome of what a bad cat who's deprived of love and barbeque is capable of. The story involves a sleazy, sexed up cat Shero, discovers he is the father of a bastard son.

172df2d17342222b2f2a9204928454e563e87a3c.title: Above the Best
172df2d17342222b2f2a9204928454e563e87a3c.synopsis: Army Aviators say they fly "above the best" see the lengths these heroes will go to, to protect the soldiers on the ground, and each other during intense combat in the most dangerous places on Earth.

286e81f4fc79c7ac38a9dfb29ae4121df7e9fcaf.title: My Days of Mercy
286e81f4fc79c7ac38a9dfb29ae4121df7e9fcaf.synopsis: The daughter of a man on death row falls in love with a woman on the opposing side of her family's political cause.

0f487448176428a12dfe48c4108d6f1468814120.title: A.M.I.
0f487448176428a12dfe48c4108d6f1468814120.synopsis: A seventeen year old girl forms a co-dependent relationship with an artificial intelligence on her phone and goes on a murderous rampage.

530dba4e15528db63edd02b5c87f138297285bf0.title: Dolls
530dba4e15528db63edd02b5c87f138297285bf0.synopsis: A struggling children's book author and his rebellious teenage daughter move into a house they've inherited and find mysterious dolls in the attic. The father and daughter soon learn that the dolls have a sinister - and deadly - past.

2b19438de9001b462731ef10a10dfcb675a4c783.title: Bittersweet Symphony
2b19438de9001b462731ef10a10dfcb675a4c783.synopsis: A musician who has just completed her first soundtrack to a Hollywood feature finds her personal life getting complicated.

d529483fa02f297ea78d9ba3369187f6a414408c.title: Ophelia
d529483fa02f297ea78d9ba3369187f6a414408c.synopsis: Ophelia comes of age as lady-in-waiting for Queen Gertrude, and her singular spirit captures Hamlet's affections. As lust and betrayal threaten the kingdom, Ophelia finds herself trapped between true love and controlling her own destiny.

9705efe642fcf14285a5edf5f329872daa210e5f.title: The 16th Episode
9705efe642fcf14285a5edf5f329872daa210e5f.synopsis: Three YouTubers struggling to get more views on their adventure channel, travel to the mythical city of Casablanca, unaware that it hides a terrifying secret.

6d3370c36e41aa9d2dc75810656f8e169c064734.title: The Last Whistle
6d3370c36e41aa9d2dc75810656f8e169c064734.synopsis: A high school football coach struggles with the fallout after one of his players dies onfield during practice.

a9ef3996c3c62197d01badfb8370b1c803698208.title: Killers Anonymous
a9ef3996c3c62197d01badfb8370b1c803698208.synopsis: A failed attempt to murder a Senator is connected to a group meeting secretly to discuss their darkest urges—to take lives.

073d00c94ad92f44c0e17d239480f5af892efc5d.title: Abduction 101
073d00c94ad92f44c0e17d239480f5af892efc5d.synopsis: Three beautiful women find a strange house in the woods. They decide to sneak in and see what's going on - They do not expect this nightmare to begin.

6020b89c23a0e5e7fe0ce256bf8e76f3ab741a59.title: Kursk
6020b89c23a0e5e7fe0ce256bf8e76f3ab741a59.synopsis: Barents Sea, August 12th, 2000. During a Russian naval exercise, and after suffering a serious accident, the K-141 Kursk submarine sinks with 118 crew members on board. While the few sailors who are still alive barely manage to survive, their families push for accurate information and a British officer struggles to obtain from the Russian government a permit to attempt a rescue before it is late. But general incompetence are against all their efforts.

e4ee51a62dc094d8f80c47f71f4ec1e41f95c327.title: Nightmare Cinema
e4ee51a62dc094d8f80c47f71f4ec1e41f95c327.synopsis: A series of down-on-their-luck individuals enter the decrepit and spine-chilling Rialto theater, only to have their deepest and darkest fears brought to life on the silver screen by The Projectionist – a mysterious, ghostly figure who holds the nightmarish futures of all who attend his screenings.

95236989865bd0935e5a6100ff1613ce46efe56d.title: The Extraordinary Journey of the Fakir
95236989865bd0935e5a6100ff1613ce46efe56d.synopsis: The story of Ajatashatru Oghash Rathod, a fakir who tricks his local village in Rajasthan, India into believing his possesses special powers and into paying him to fly to Paris to buy a bed of nails from an Ikea store.

713e6018d1e90d8ada4600b62425b34d15bd3562.title: Escape Plan: The Extractors
713e6018d1e90d8ada4600b62425b34d15bd3562.synopsis: After security expert Ray Breslin is hired to rescue the kidnapped daughter of a Hong Kong tech mogul from a formidable Latvian prison, Breslin's girlfriend is also captured. Now he and his team must pull off a deadly rescue mission to confront their sadistic foe and save the hostages before time runs out.

257c20466a3c0f3e80e6d4b56836a938bab5d1db.title: In Full Bloom
257c20466a3c0f3e80e6d4b56836a938bab5d1db.synopsis: Set shortly after the end of World War II, IN FULL BLOOM is a philosophical boxing drama of two fighters from opposite worlds (USA and Japan) who are pulled together for a questionable fight arranged by their unscrupulous managers and the Yakuza.

654072b1ee80ca4c4bc0e598e2143e8ca864159a.title: Disappearance
654072b1ee80ca4c4bc0e598e2143e8ca864159a.synopsis: After the Author George Boulangé disappears from his sailboat one night, Detective Kenny Park must try to ascertain what happened by interviewing his wife, girlfriend and captain.

e4ea52021a8324001f1601b8d5172f9cfa5d7a14.title: Submission
e4ea52021a8324001f1601b8d5172f9cfa5d7a14.synopsis: After two marines make it home following an ISIS interrogation, one struggles to survive while the other fights his way back into the mixed martial arts world that he left behind years ago.

547c1fb2ee471849a6b997396fcbe0f16de06ce3.title: Murder Mystery
547c1fb2ee471849a6b997396fcbe0f16de06ce3.synopsis: After attending a gathering on a billionaire's yacht during a European vacation, a New York cop and his wife become prime suspects when he's murdered.

acd7da12b049809c58d4f571077e1bf981db3580.title: Daughter of the Wolf
acd7da12b049809c58d4f571077e1bf981db3580.synopsis: Ex-military specialist Clair Hamilton returns home from her tour in the Middle East due to her father's passing and to claim her inheritance. Her son is then kidnapped and held for ransom by a gang led by a mysterious figure known only as “Father”.

9155dc602eef1e31d8eb66ff4fa4454695eda987.title: Deep Murder
9155dc602eef1e31d8eb66ff4fa4454695eda987.synopsis: Set in an alternate reality in which everyone is a cliché from a tacky soft-core porn film, a group of increasingly self-aware stock characters are up against a mysterious killer offing them one by one.

c5cfc09ce3768bee32ae7b8af1a598b2fa841f5c.title: Shaft
c5cfc09ce3768bee32ae7b8af1a598b2fa841f5c.synopsis: JJ, aka John Shaft Jr., may be a cyber security expert with a degree from MIT, but to uncover the truth behind his best friend’s untimely death, he needs an education only his dad can provide. Absent throughout JJ’s youth, the legendary locked-and-loaded John Shaft agrees to help his progeny navigate Harlem’s heroin-infested underbelly.

c93e0cff02f9d8b448a143f21bc5e06ca5ac0149.title: Our Time
c93e0cff02f9d8b448a143f21bc5e06ca5ac0149.synopsis: A family lives in the Mexican countryside raising fighting bulls. Esther is in charge of running the ranch, while her husband Juan, a world-renowned poet, raises and selects the beasts. Although in an open marriage, their relationship begins to crumble when Esther falls in love with an American horsebreaker and Juan is unable to control his jealousy.

473fb59de2e137c0e859985705e784246190d586.title: Clinton Road
473fb59de2e137c0e859985705e784246190d586.synopsis: A widowed firefighter seeks closure after his wife goes missing on an actual haunted road in rural New Jersey but must unlock the roads secret if he wants to get out alive.

d791e5f6a17d9ab49f6c96fd73ca30d10c05930b.title: Hollow Point
d791e5f6a17d9ab49f6c96fd73ca30d10c05930b.synopsis: When his wife and daughter are senselessly murdered, a grieving man finds himself caught up in a war between a group of charismatic vigilantes and the crime that infests their city.

ec74a8e284c14a75e07592f1cd4782681f09c18c.title: Strange Events 2
ec74a8e284c14a75e07592f1cd4782681f09c18c.synopsis: Another grab bag of horror shorts tossed together into an anthology package.

2ee5c2aa605542763e1eaa084d979cba9a40bb95.title: Norm of the North: King Sized Adventure
2ee5c2aa605542763e1eaa084d979cba9a40bb95.synopsis: An ancient Chinese artifact has been stolen by a villainous archaeologist named Dexter. With the help of his Lemming friends, Norm must keep his word and embark on a journey across the world to help recover the artifact for the people of China.

3df15e9ad6fee21256aee552b2910243e88829fc.title: Project Ithaca
3df15e9ad6fee21256aee552b2910243e88829fc.synopsis: Five strangers awaken to find themselves trapped aboard an alien spaceship that seems to be harnessing their terror to power the ship. They begin to understand that these species have been abducting humans for decades and possibly centuries.

392aa8afae3183a5e7a4dea18343619da6f008ec.title: Last Summer
392aa8afae3183a5e7a4dea18343619da6f008ec.synopsis: During a long hot summer in the 1970s, four boys roam free through a neglected rural paradise, until a tragedy strikes that sets them against the adult world and changes their lives forever.

8cea47d4108b24f0e474f79c140d2d8583b54a07.title: Changeland
8cea47d4108b24f0e474f79c140d2d8583b54a07.synopsis: Follow two estranged best friends on an epic, life-changing adventure in Thailand as they're reminded that there's no problem that friendship and a few rounds in a Muay Thai boxing ring can't fix.

7fc5eb6b8e0b55e9fc85f83b4f3b93f421d3d769.title: I Am Mother
7fc5eb6b8e0b55e9fc85f83b4f3b93f421d3d769.synopsis: A teenage girl is raised underground by a robot "Mother", designed to repopulate the earth following an extinction event. But their unique bond is threatened when an inexplicable stranger arrives with alarming news.

62d607d390e04a6beb9b70086ff3d234d14eb7f3.title: Vault
62d607d390e04a6beb9b70086ff3d234d14eb7f3.synopsis: A group of small time criminals in 1975 attempt to pull off the biggest heist in American history; stealing over $30 million from the Mafia in the smallest state in the union, Rhode Island.

aff603c054be8ad88c6654c0bc42a5e04ade504a.title: Diggerz: Black Lung Rises
aff603c054be8ad88c6654c0bc42a5e04ade504a.synopsis: An evil creature attacks a small mining town. A college student and a cranky outcast must uncover the mystery of the creature's past to put an end to the bloodshed.

cd7f5322ac2e6664d1e0715f1600d086983658d1.title: The Wind
cd7f5322ac2e6664d1e0715f1600d086983658d1.synopsis: A supernatural thriller set in the Western frontier of the late 1800s, The Wind stars Caitlin Gerard as a plains-woman driven mad by the harshness and isolation of the untamed land.

6bb40fd6975752f39502d7435c59593c34926de8.title: Made in Malta
6bb40fd6975752f39502d7435c59593c34926de8.synopsis: An American filmmaker in Malta has a life-changing encounter with a Spanish lover who walked out five years earlier.

2e22616fabff59e1c8d33baea61d91039172482f.title: A Haunting at Silver Falls: The Return
2e22616fabff59e1c8d33baea61d91039172482f.synopsis: Several years after a deadly struggle with her serial killer aunt, Jordan works to escape her troubled history. But when her aunt's revenge-seeking specter surfaces to join forces with a deranged convict, Jordan must return to the haunted town of Silver Falls for a final showdown with the ghosts of her past

60b8442e3237a709c1d5f1947be0b10abdc4a8cf.title: The Possession Diaries
60b8442e3237a709c1d5f1947be0b10abdc4a8cf.synopsis: Playing with a Ouija board is dangerous, and college student Rebecca Clarkson is now documenting the proof, as day by day a demon takes possession of her while a webcam audience watch the horrific event.

78701237d71e19f3f7f7f06e99f03a78d8b0a26b.title: The Russian Bride
78701237d71e19f3f7f7f06e99f03a78d8b0a26b.synopsis: A Russian woman travels to America with her daughter to marry a reclusive billionaire, who turns out to be a psycho who sends their lives spiraling into a living hell.

cc0fd9d6033749d7328f7d97d99e15c42790e070.title: Miranda Sings Live... Your Welcome.
cc0fd9d6033749d7328f7d97d99e15c42790e070.synopsis: Viral video star Miranda Sings and her real-world alter ego Colleen Ballinger share the stage in a special packed with music, comedy and "magichinry."

3ef35d5a91c1863e4c6074c2f7845274c7a816db.title: #FollowMe
3ef35d5a91c1863e4c6074c2f7845274c7a816db.synopsis: Three British women from London, consisting of a YouTuber and her two friends, go missing from a motel in California while travelling from Los Angeles to San Francisco after posting on social media using the the hashtag #followme.

f8d37dc1921fd01d46e999e76e1cac3a1f3a81ec.title: Recovery
f8d37dc1921fd01d46e999e76e1cac3a1f3a81ec.synopsis: The patients and staff of a secluded heroin treatment center must do battle with more than their own demons as a mysterious killer begins picking them off one-by-one.

d757497f9b34ad39542795b169b35a8f0920d4a7.title: Robert Reborn
d757497f9b34ad39542795b169b35a8f0920d4a7.synopsis: In 1951 USSR, as the Cold War intensifies, infamous dictator Joseph Stalin is suffering with illness and his death is imminent. Meanwhile, KGB agent Stoichkov discovers a mysterious stage show in the Baltic region featuring three creepy dolls - Robert, Kalashnikov and Miss Cyclops. Spellbound by the lifelike animation displayed by the dolls on stage, Stoichkov investigates the show's host and discovers he is a German Toymaker who owns a mystical book which holds the key to eternal life. Believing the Toymaker and his book will help Stalin escape death, Stoichkov kidnaps him and they board a plane to Moscow. But the Toymaker's living creations have followed them. When the plane is in mid air all hell breaks loose as Stoichkov and his team of KGB agents realize the three dolls are on board and will stop at nothing to rescue their puppet master. Fasten your seat belt and prepare for blood soaked toy terror at 30,000 feet.

8e29ee7af9016c2367d766d84daafbcee93ca6ba.title: Colourblind
8e29ee7af9016c2367d766d84daafbcee93ca6ba.synopsis: A reluctant private investigator is hired to track the tail of a suspected suicidal girl.

8bd9890ff6c023d2a4ca8060bb88f5135dc5e0cb.title: Owned: A Tale of Two Americas
8bd9890ff6c023d2a4ca8060bb88f5135dc5e0cb.synopsis: A fever dream vision into the dark history behind the US housing economy. Tracking its overtly racist beginnings to its unbridled commoditization, the doc exposes a foundational story few Americans understand as their own.

09a0688c0076e906d9f2e0964a4113e521de0954.title: The Odds
09a0688c0076e906d9f2e0964a4113e521de0954.synopsis: A young woman enlists in an underground game of pain endurance in the hope of winning the million dollar prize. She soon learns the real opponent is the man who's running the game, as he employs horrific methods to manipulate and defeat her.

515b5ec52c0e20f4d913cf5d6b9765a2b6f7693b.title: Mollywood
515b5ec52c0e20f4d913cf5d6b9765a2b6f7693b.synopsis: A serial killer disguises himself as a drug dealer in order to "deliver" young people their worshiped drugs. The serial killer is simultaneously tracked by a determined detective in the city.

de81eba53097d9cedca6e8188f0c67fae6c27609.title: Crisis Hotline
de81eba53097d9cedca6e8188f0c67fae6c27609.synopsis: A race-against-time psychosexual thriller that highlights the potentially darkest sides of the social media phenomenon. Jaded by the job of managing an LGBT crisis line, Simon (Corey Jackson) finds that most of his callers are using the service for reasons that would qualify as being certainly less than a crisis. That all changes when he gets a call from Danny (Christian Gabriel) who says he is in the process of killing himself. Instantly gripped by his first real case, Simon does his best to connect with Danny and find out why he has come to consider such a drastic action. As the tale of Danny's journey is unravelled through the use of flashback sequences, we discover a young romance, a troubling network of individuals, and a dark secret.

0d64db533dfbc9fbcd063d6c25588de8e4a309da.title: Deadwood: The Movie
0d64db533dfbc9fbcd063d6c25588de8e4a309da.synopsis: Follow the 10-year reunion of the Deadwood camp to celebrate South Dakota's statehood. Former rivalries are reignited, alliances are tested and old wounds are reopened, as all are left to navigate the inevitable changes that modernity and time have wrought.

003185132650395c1bfff6d0bdfd8f71ef916945.title: Domino
003185132650395c1bfff6d0bdfd8f71ef916945.synopsis: Seeking justice for his partner’s murder by an ISIS member, a Copenhagen police officer finds himself caught in a cat and mouse game with a duplicitous CIA agent who is using the killer as a pawn to trap other ISIS members.

286e81f4fc79c7ac38a9dfb29ae4121df7e9fcaf.title: My Days of Mercy
286e81f4fc79c7ac38a9dfb29ae4121df7e9fcaf.synopsis: The daughter of a man on death row falls in love with a woman on the opposing side of her family's political cause.

44a264d171ae8521b6ef1e618ba90e072826bd38.title: Stranger Things
44a264d171ae8521b6ef1e618ba90e072826bd38.synopsis: When a young boy disappears, his mother, a police chief, and his friends must confront terrifying forces in order to get him back.

episodes.overview: Summer brings new jobs and budding romance. But the mood shifts when Dustin's radio picks up a Russian broadcast, and Will senses something is wrong.
episodes.title: Chapter One: Suzie, Do You Copy?

episodes.overview: Nancy and Jonathan follow a lead, Steve and Robin sign on to a secret mission, and Max and Eleven go shopping. A rattled Billy has troubling visions.
episodes.title: Chapter Two: The Mall Rats

episodes.overview: With El and Max looking for Billy, Will declares a day without girls. Steve and Dustin go on a stakeout, and Joyce and Hopper return to Hawkins Lab.
episodes.title: Chapter Three: The Case of the Missing Lifeguard

episodes.overview: A code red brings the gang back together to face a frighteningly familiar evil. Karen urges Nancy to keep digging, and Robin finds a useful map.
episodes.title: Chapter Four: The Sauna Test

episodes.overview: Strange surprises lurk inside an old farmhouse and deep beneath the Starcourt Mall. Meanwhile, the Mind Flayer is gathering strength.
episodes.title: Chapter Five: The Flayed

episodes.overview: Dr. Alexei reveals what the Russians have been building, and Eleven sees where Billy has been. Dustin and Erica stage a daring rescue.
episodes.title: Chapter Six: E Pluribus Unum

episodes.overview: With time running out -- and an assassin close behind -- Hopper's crew races back to Hawkins, where El and the kids are preparing for war.
episodes.title: Chapter Seven: The Bite

episodes.overview: Terror reigns in the food court when the Mind Flayer comes to collect. But down below, in the dark, the future of the world is at stake.
episodes.title: Chapter Eight: The Battle of Starcourt

episodes.overview: On his way home from a friend's house, young Will sees something terrifying. Nearby, a sinister secret lurks in the depths of a government lab.
episodes.title: Chapter One: The Vanishing of Will Byers

episodes.overview: Lucas, Mike and Dustin try to talk to the girl they found in the woods. Hopper questions an anxious Joyce about an unsettling phone call.
episodes.title: Chapter Two: The Weirdo on Maple Street

episodes.overview: An increasingly concerned Nancy looks for Barb and finds out what Jonathan's been up to. Joyce is convinced Will is trying to talk to her.
episodes.title: Chapter Three: Holly, Jolly

episodes.overview: Refusing to believe Will is dead, Joyce tries to connect with her son. The boys give Eleven a makeover. Nancy and Jonathan form an unlikely alliance.
episodes.title: Chapter Four: The Body

episodes.overview: Hopper breaks into the lab while Nancy and Jonathan confront the force that took Will. The boys ask Mr. Clarke how to travel to another dimension.
episodes.title: Chapter Five: The Flea and the Acrobat

episodes.overview: A frantic Jonathan looks for Nancy in the darkness, but Steve's looking for her, too. Hopper and Joyce uncover the truth about the lab's experiments.
episodes.title: Chapter Six: The Monster

episodes.overview: Eleven struggles to reach Will, while Lucas warns that "the bad men are coming." Nancy and Jonathan show the police what Jonathan caught on camera.
episodes.title: Chapter Seven: The Bathtub

episodes.overview: Dr. Brenner holds Hopper and Joyce for questioning while the boys wait with Eleven in the gym. Back at Will's, Nancy and Jonathan prepare for battle.
episodes.title: Chapter Eight: The Upside Down

episodes.overview: As the town preps for Halloween, a high-scoring rival shakes things up at the arcade, and a skeptical Hopper inspects a field of rotting pumpkins.
episodes.title: Chapter One: MADMAX

episodes.overview: After Will sees something terrible on trick-or-treat night, Mike wonders whether Eleven's still out there. Nancy wrestles with the truth about Barb.
episodes.title: Chapter Two: Trick or Treat, Freak

episodes.overview: Dustin adopts a strange new pet, and Eleven grows increasingly impatient. A well-meaning Bob urges Will to stand up to his fears.
episodes.title: Chapter Three: The Pollywog

episodes.overview: An ailing Will opens up to Joyce -- with disturbing results. While Hopper digs for the truth, Eleven unearths a surprising discovery.
episodes.title: Chapter Four: Will the Wise

episodes.overview: Nancy and Jonathan swap conspiracy theories with a new ally as Eleven searches for someone from her past. “Bob the Brain” tackles a difficult problem.
episodes.title: Chapter Five: Dig Dug

episodes.overview: Will's connection to a shadowy evil grows stronger, but no one's quite sure how to stop it. Elsewhere, Dustin and Steve forge an unlikely bond.
episodes.title: Chapter Six: The Spy

episodes.overview: Psychic visions draw Eleven to a band of violent outcasts and an angry girl with a shadowy past.
episodes.title: Chapter Seven: The Lost Sister

episodes.overview: An unlikely hero steps forward when a deadly development puts the Hawkins Lab on lockdown, trapping Will and several others inside.
episodes.title: Chapter Eight: The Mind Flayer

episodes.overview: Eleven makes plans to finish what she started while the survivors turn up the heat on the monstrous force that's holding Will hostage.
episodes.title: Chapter Nine: The Gate
